QEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"因不同券商公司對於入金的要求不同，有些券商要求快速入金，有些公司要求精準匹配銀行流水後再入金，綜合考慮了上述因素，系統兼容了2套入金的流程，如下：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpBNnmLNFfujKoTwtwtTSJdc","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":738,"token":"TUambKCm8owhAGx4veujeMLTpUh","width":2940},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjp3TlN1qhTpcpbwlgBpy7nqg","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"前置条件","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpT259Tc0WczFQabUqMCkg7d","block_type":2,"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"無","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpEpLSCtbFWrFyTNp6mpruyu","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"二、操作說明","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpXSbnGvu9ACYNi55WbKKCGh","block_type":19,"callout":{"background_color":5,"border_color":5,"emoji_id":"round_pushpin","text_color":1},"children":["doxjpOpk1fdmNk1AO9o2bIOiKre"],"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpOpk1fdmNk1AO9o2bIOiKre","block_type":2,"parent_id":"doxjpXSbnGvu9ACYNi55WbKKCGh","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"菜單入口：款項管理-入金","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpvatJvMQOeJUFmoZgBFtKQh","block_type":4,"heading2":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"入金申請","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpUjSwSWdfzGh7jf04XJF8Ya","block_type":2,"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"入金申請為用戶方提出，申請的內容包含了幣種、申請金額、收款銀行卡與備註4大部分。WHALE使用者可以手動幫助客戶進行證券入倉并根據客戶提交的申請進行駁回、提交審批等操作。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpty8nHASNzbDUlet8JYcyOd","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"新建(入金申請)","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpUmX0t0RCSzTaGCvVgYEmre","block_type":2,"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"適用於使用者聯絡後台操作員進行手動入金的場景，操作員需要依序選擇客戶並輸入金的幣種、方式、收款銀行、金額、備註、憑證（如有）","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjp7xMAHWs4uowrTSCLwfYEDb","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1000,"token":"ShmgbBWaOoi7xPxNEIRjH0pZpue","width":2074},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpeMRvPqbpQpQsH4pDuRmF9f","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"駁回：若客戶遞交的入金申請資料有誤或使用者反饋本次申請無效時，操作員可以進行【駁回】操作","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpK802QXtGbXreKHW5Agcn2Y","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"删除：若客戶遞交的入金申請資料有誤或使用者反饋本次申請無效時，操作員也可以透過【删除】按鈕直接刪除目標記錄","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpTMktFWubbtenN4mH5Wul1J","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"修改：若在提交入金申請前，發現客戶遞交的某筆入金申請有問題，可在與客戶確認無誤後可以透過【編輯】按鈕進行修正，修改後需進行工單審批，審批通過後修改內容生效。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"children":["doxjpGHUQ2f4exXvgY05xhNCEEh","doxjpAvCDeBnHq8FsNPXzGgieVc"],"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpGHUQ2f4exXvgY05xhNCEEh","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":998,"token":"JJc1bPTaRoOoFFx9iepjvxOjpVe","width":2076},"parent_id":"doxjpTMktFWubbtenN4mH5Wul1J"},{"block_id":"doxjpAvCDeBnHq8FsNPXzGgieVc","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"修改的范围：幣種、入金方式、收款銀行、金額、入金手續費、備註、憑證（重新上傳）","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxjpTMktFWubbtenN4mH5Wul1J"},{"block_id":"doxjp9jvgf7CkiTnFx80IujQonh","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"提交（","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"可批量操作","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"）：經過操作人員初步審查無誤後，可以將申請提交至下一節點的操作人員進行審核-提現操作","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpZCPDjvk07Sad7KlhT6PH70","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"直接入帳：由於不同券商使用者對於入金的時效性要求不同，直接入帳可以幫助使用者快速處理入金流程，使用者接收到客戶的入金申請後只需補充銀行流水資訊即可完成入帳。直接入帳預設需要進行審批，如果不需要審核可聯絡運維人員進行配置。","text_element_style"