ontent":"入金匹配","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpa24rJw6bTW7OuANuxODWTg","block_type":2,"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"此頁面的數據皆來自銀行帳單中的入金帳單，若券商的業務規範需要銀行流水與入金記錄匹配一直後進行入帳，在確認銀行流水資訊已同步系統後，可手動在入金匹配頁面下處理。處理的方式分為：關聯入帳、退還客戶2大類。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpJMMNA1cHwwUiof4I5mLOzd","block_type":30,"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d","sheet":{"token":"U1rVsDGanhzv3UtASsej3R5xp0b_KQVWZi"}},{"block_id":"doxjpsG0tubjgYVZfGqwgXBFGOf","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"關聯：僅入金的銀行賬單中系統無法自動匹配需要人工操作的記錄，在此頁面下操作員可以根據系統提示進行確認，並進行後續入賬或者其他操作。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"children":["doxjpdGAXQ0puuuqZb9sGedJ2jf"],"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpdGAXQ0puuuqZb9sGedJ2jf","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"關聯頁面將根據姓名配對用戶自動比對欄位（如圖），確認無誤後可點選【關聯】","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxjpsG0tubjgYVZfGqwgXBFGOf"},{"block_id":"doxjp85UBATYYdd9RiS3H6cpz2g","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1842,"token":"AjoebS1tLoumPtxvOVtjZLI1p6d","width":3818},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpr48OeSxl0Y3ISb8tCtZD5e","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1950,"token":"YIAtbP6S4o2cevxWt9GjlVq2pzh","width":3904},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpDJsgSSfoBcnyAqNDyuMWtg","block_type":14,"code":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"- 如係統預設匹配的用戶不準，可透過【自定義】手動關聯該筆銀行流水所對應的客戶。關聯的方式有：入金的申請與證券帳號","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"language":1,"wrap":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpl736IjsghSB0EPaHNtGNFh","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1776,"token":"TBpgbcEFUozISUxccdpjbuVFpcg","width":3308},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpRUJOqCcwJzzI6DVMjz35tg","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1750,"token":"XAzEbmIDcogUT3x0gf7jrpgCpIe","width":3308},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpBwCyTsaBakctA1qILVt3Df","block_type":2,"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"入金退還：若因種種原因，導致入金未能正常進入客戶的證券帳戶，需要對這筆記錄進行退款時，可以使用該功能進行操作。用戶需填寫客戶的銀行卡訊息，確認無誤後點選【確定】流轉至入金審核頁面進行審核操作。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpZtyJahRHex5bQxodLY0ame","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1326,"token":"NryQbXcMGoFJVyxBEdMjge96pjc","width":2436},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpLpSCxAG5yGyn03qbFAOL3e","block_type":2,"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"出金退還：由於入金匹配頁面的數據來自銀行流水流入的信息，如果用戶在處理客户出金的時候被銀行拒絕，在銀行流水中會以流入的形式存在，用戶需要關聯出金的業務流水號通過【出金退還】功能處理此類記錄。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpXxrmrOrmZAMbrjv3rzuYST","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1234,"token":"XXvmbr0PuoGCrdx06NKjDsGJpmh","width":2366},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpEVPX3wxQcolJYBQX9eWPVc","block_type":4,"heading2":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"入金審核","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpCIwUnk7fJToex94g1BZLye","block_type":2,"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"用戶在「入金匹配」頁面中依賴銀行流水流入的資訊進行處理後，下游的審核人員會對處理的結果進行審批，通過后方可入帳。對於正常關聯入帳的入金，由於存在客戶在入金時時證券帳戶仍在客戶中的情況，後台將針對這類記錄單獨進行審批。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpXQseUFqg8VKPFQxjiQMn2b","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"開戶中：選取目標記錄後，點選【審批】後進入詳情頁面再次核對訊息，確認無誤後發起工單審批","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpu1KdEuDbenc2WEgDrPIXTh","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1598,"token":"UV59bZvGXoRgqKxmBADj3r43pEh","width":3334},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpMdJH2V4Ul6vIbdFDfdXGLb","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"已開戶：選取目標記錄後，點選【審批】後進入詳情頁面再次核對訊息，確認無誤後審核通過","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpTQuIL2dpRdkKAKj0abzq09","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1598,"token":"CraHbYLHwof34wxnp44j8L3op7c","width":3318},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjp98DYZXzjVrYzE8jxt6czec","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"入金退還：選取目標記錄後，點選【審批】後喚出審批工單，確認資訊無誤後審核通過","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"MQEJdkoHxoLMvVxTBd1jw0Cqp0d"},{"block_id":"doxjpgnEE2CkeBkAf9rRoJDeK4c","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1596,"token":"T3zWbyL0qowzTzxrD5wjffgqpWh","width":3330},"p